<h2>4. Start using Portus Home</h2>
<p>
	You can now start using Portus Home, wherever you are, no  matter whether you are home or away. When you are out of your home, you can connect through your phone or Internet browser. When you are at home, you can also use your phone, wall panel, remote etc to view and control you home.
</p>
